Dear Raffaella,

Documents

We have included the documents as requested.

The documents are released to you on the basis that it contains personal in=
formation that you are entitled to receive under the Privacy Act 2020.  Due=
 to the confidential nature of that information, Tower requires that you do=
 not disclose the information provided to you by Tower's staff to any third=
 parties, without Tower's prior written consent.

Note that if the personal information held by Tower is incorrect, you may r=
equest correction of that information.

If you have any further questions or concerns, please contact us on 0800 80=
8 808.

Please use the link below to get access
https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-sc393b8aa6fe64f69b68334ef28b2cb7a

